2nd Call for Papers

Dear  Colleague,

On 14-16 May 2010, we are very proud to be organizing "The 6th Internationa=
l ELT
Research Conference" with the chosen theme of: Current Trends in SLA Resear=
ch
and Language Teaching in Ephesus/Sel=E7uk, Izmir/Turkey. The conference is
